H2\\/iphone-xr-17.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/fptshop.com.vn\\/Uploads\\/images\\/2015\\/Tin-Tuc\\/QuanLNH2\\/iphone-xr-17.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>Nh\\u1eadn di\\u1ec7n khu&ocirc;n m\\u1eb7t Face ID n&acirc;ng cao<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">B\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>iPhone XR<\\/strong>&nbsp;\\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n v&agrave; an to&agrave;n h\\u01a1n bao gi\\u1edd h\\u1ebft khi m\\u1eadt kh\\u1ea9u ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; khu&ocirc;n m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n. B\\u1ea1n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 m\\u1edf kh&oacute;a iPhone, \\u0111\\u0103ng nh\\u1eadp v&agrave;o \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng hay thanh to&aacute;n ch\\u1ec9 trong nh&aacute;y m\\u1eaft m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\\u1ea7n nh\\u1eadp m\\u1eadt kh\\u1ea9u. \\u0110&acirc;y l&agrave; ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u1ee9c b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt an to&agrave;n nh\\u1ea5t tr&ecirc;n smartphone v&agrave; n&oacute; c&ograve;n nhanh h\\u01a1n n\\u1eefa tr&ecirc;n iPhone XR.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" data-original=\\\"https:\\/\\/fptshop.com.vn\\/Uploads\\/images\\/2015\\/Tin-Tuc\\/QuanLNH2\\/iphone-xr-11.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/fptshop.com.vn\\/Uploads\\/images\\/2015\\/Tin-Tuc\\/QuanLNH2\\/iphone-xr-11.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>Apple A12 Bionic, con chip th&ocirc;ng minh v&agrave; m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd nh\\u1ea5t<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>iPhone XR<\\/strong>&nbsp;\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb con chip A12 Bionic c&oacute; 6 nh&acirc;n, trong \\u0111&oacute; 2 nh&acirc;n hi\\u1ec7u n\\u0103ng cao nhanh h\\u01a1n 15% v&agrave; 4 nh&acirc;n ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111i\\u1ec7n ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m h\\u01a1n 50% so v\\u1edbi th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc A11 Bionic c\\u1ee7a iPhone X. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi GPU \\u0111\\u1ed3 h\\u1ecda c\\u1ee7a A12 Bionic m\\u1ea1nh h\\u01a1n t\\u1edbi 50%, cho ph&eacute;p b\\u1ea1n ch\\u01a1i m\\u1ecdi t\\u1ef1a game \\u1edf c\\u1ea5u h&igrave;nh cao nh\\u1ea5t m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch nh\\u1eb9 nh&agrave;ng v&agrave; m\\u01b0\\u1ee3t m&agrave;.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" data-original=\\\"https:\\/\\/fptshop.com.vn\\/Uploads\\/images\\/2015\\/Tin-Tuc\\/QuanLNH2\\/iphone-xr-12.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/fptshop.com.vn\\/Uploads\\/images\\/2015\\/Tin-Tuc\\/QuanLNH2\\/iphone-xr-12.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">Kh&ocirc;ng ch\\u1ec9 m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd, \\u0111i\\u1ec3m kh&aacute;c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a A12 Bionic c&ograve;n \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb s\\u1ef1 th&ocirc;ng minh c\\u1ee7a con chip n&agrave;y. V\\u1edbi 8 nh&acirc;n Neural Engine c&oacute; kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ecfi theo th\\u1eddi gian th\\u1ef1c, iPhone XR c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eadn ra th&oacute;i quen s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a 