\\u1ea1, thu h&uacute;t m\\u1ecdi &aacute;nh nh&igrave;n. Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf n&agrave;y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ho&agrave;n thi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ec9 m\\u1ec9 nh\\u1edd nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng bo cong tinh t\\u1ebf, ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn v&agrave; li\\u1ec1n l\\u1ea1c. Nh\\u1edd m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh vi\\u1ec1n m\\u1ecfng t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u n&ecirc;n Galaxy A21s kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; l\\u1edbn m&agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ea1i, r\\u1ea5t v\\u1eeba v\\u1eb7n trong l&ograve;ng b\\u1ea1n tay b\\u1ea1n. S\\u1ebd c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn m&agrave;u tr\\u1ebb trung nh\\u01b0 \\u0110en, Tr\\u1eafng hay Xanh ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi c&aacute; t&iacute;nh m\\u1ed7i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><img alt=\\\"thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf Samsung Galaxy A21s\\\" data-original=\\\"https:\\/\\/images.fpt.shop\\/unsafe\\/fit-in\\/filters:quality(90)\\/fptshop.com.vn\\/Uploads\\/images\\/2015\\/Tin-Tuc\\/QuanLNH2\\/samsung-galaxy-a21s-3.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/images.fpt.shop\\/unsafe\\/fit-in\\/filters:quality(90)\\/fptshop.com.vn\\/Uploads\\/images\\/2015\\/Tin-Tuc\\/QuanLNH2\\/samsung-galaxy-a21s-3.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><b>B\\u1ed9 t\\u1ee9 camera sau 48MP huy\\u1ec1n \\u1ea3o, \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh<\\/b><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n l&agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh, ch\\u1eafc h\\u1eb3n b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd r\\u1ea5t h\\u1ee9ng th&uacute; v\\u1edbi Samsung Galaxy A21s. Tha h\\u1ed3 s&aacute;ng t\\u1ea1o, tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i bi\\u1ebfn h&oacute;a v\\u1edbi 4 camera sau tr&ecirc;n chi\\u1ebfc \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea7y th&uacute; v\\u1ecb n&agrave;y. B&ecirc;n c\\u1ea1nh camera ch&iacute;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9 ph&acirc;n gi\\u1ea3i l&ecirc;n t\\u1edbi 48MP, Galaxy 