g c&aacute;ch b&igrave;nh lun ph&iacute;a di nh&eacute;!</p>', 'tren-tay-oppo-reno3-camera-selfie-dem-44mp-zoom-20x-dau-tien-phan-khuc-tam-trung-1588836378.jpg', 1588836378, 1588784400, 2, 'vi', 0, 'tren-tay-oppo-reno3-camera-selfie-dem-44mp-zoom-20x', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL);
